Chile ‘Proactive Enough’ to Face Global Crisis, De Gregorio Says

-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w   a n d   R a n d a l l   W o o d s
-- 
2011-09-22T23:34:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/chile-proactive-enough-to-face-global-crisis-de-gregorio-says.html
Chile ’s monetary policy is flexible
and proactive enough to face the deteriorating global outlook,
central bank President Jose De Gregorio said in an interview in
 Washington  today.  “I’m very confident that we will make the decisions on
time,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
